  # New Rate of Public Lighting Tax
  
  [Rajah & Tann Sok & Heng Law Office](https://www.lexology.com/contributors/rajah-and-tann-asia)
  
  [![Rajah & Tann Asia logo](https://files.lexology.com/images/lexology/firm/new/3f032b4b-e332-463d-8cfe-033c725a9f3c/W350/20241128054454.png)](http://www.rajahtann.com/)
  
  [![Heng Chhay](https://files.lexology.com/images/lexology/authorv2/squaretop/3b427738-78d9-4263-976b-958df5382109/W100/H100/20251117162134/photo.jpg)](https://www.lexology.com/2319/author/Heng_Chhay/)
  
