  [![Chum Socheat](https://files.lexology.com/images/lexology/authorv2/squaretop/37693f2d-a08e-4929-8cb0-7489c7096923/W100/H100/20220103091716/photo.jpg)](https://www.lexology.com/2319/author/CHUM_Socheat/)
  
